        <Document ID="29B72BA6-EE6B-40FA-8116-59D775FE1702">
            <Title>2B: EVEN MORE EXCUSES</Title>
            <Text>2B: EVEN MORE EXCUSES

If only C1 made excuses earlier, this is where you could show C2’s excuses for why they absolutely shouldn’t be in love with C1. Otherwise, restate why they think it really would be a terrible idea for them to be in a relationship. Their existing problems are still there and they’re the reason why C1 (or both C1 and C2) can’t open their heart for love.

You can share more of their backstory here, but don’t infodump. Remember, the backstory is most effective when it’s casting a shadow, so make that shadow effective before you go and tell your readers everything you think they should know.
</Text>
